19
00:01:46,980 --> 00:01:55,710
These essential services such as water supply,
power supply, sanitation are interconnected, no electricity, no water.

20
00:01:56,900 --> 00:02:03,740
This interconnectivity between essential services
needs to be understood and properly integrated into humanitarian

21
