22
00:02:08,580 --> 00:02:13,960
Urban services require three elements
in order to function: people, hardware

23
00:02:14,000 --> 00:02:18,590
and consumables.
Disruption to an essential service occurs

24
00:02:18,760 --> 00:02:24,490
