from explosive munitions attract the most attention

27
00:02:40,470 --> 00:02:44,870
but field experiments suggest that the
cumulative impact is the most destructive

28
00:02:44,910 --> 00:02:46,910
and the most difficult to recover from.

29
00:02:48,440 --> 00:02:54,230
Humanitarian response in urban areas is
a major challenge of today's humanitarian crisis.

